      { titles:["anger with a point","use it"], bodies:["anger at unfairness that goes nowhere becomes bitterness. let it move you — even toward acceptance.","you saw something wrong. that clarity is real even when the situation isn't fixable."], tips:["write down exactly what was unfair and why it matters to you","ask honestly: is there anything I can do, even something small?","if not, set a date to let it go — not today, but a real date"] }
